OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,FA second north Wales council has
OL,7,Fdeclared a "health emergency" over
OL,8,F"third world" conditions for patients.
OL,10,FConwy County Borough Council's
OL,11,Fdecision follows a similar motion
OL,12,Fvoted through by Denbighshire County
OL,13,FCouncil in November last year over
OL,14,Fpatients under Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,15,FUniversity Health Board (BCUHB).
