OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,FCouncil leader Julie Fallon backed a
OL,7,F"notice of motion" at a meeting on
OL,8,FThursday which comes as all six of the
OL,9,Fregion's county councils raised
OL,10,Fconcerns about the spread of "corridor
OL,11,Fcare" throughout north Wales hospitals.
OL,13,FCllr Fallon said the health board's
OL,14,Fchief executive, Carol Shillabeer, and
OL,15,Fthe Welsh Government Health Minister,
OL,16,FJeremy Miles, failed to respond to a
OL,17,Fletter sent on behalf of all six
OL,18,Fauthorities, raising concerns about
OL,19,Fthe standard of healthcare in north
OL,20,FWales.
