OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,FThe letter was signed by all six
OL,7,Fcouncil leaders and sought
OL,8,Fclarification over whether "a new
OL,9,Fpolicy has been introduced" placing
OL,10,Fpatients "in corridors all night on
OL,11,Fwards in north Wales's three major
OL,12,Fhospitals".
OL,14,FConwy councillors backed the notice of
OL,15,Fmotion declaring the emergency, which
OL,16,Fwas tabled by Cllr Cheryl Carlisle at
OL,17,Fa full council meeting on Thursday.
