OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,FIt warned that health services in the
OL,7,Fregion are "in crisis" and demanded
OL,8,Furgent action. The motion calls for
OL,9,Fcommunity hospital beds to be
OL,10,Freopened, an end to corridor care in
OL,11,Femergency departments, an immediate
OL,12,Fhalt to premature patient discharges,
OL,13,Fand the reinstatement of the stalled
OL,14,FConwy West Health Centre project and
OL,15,Fits funding.
