OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,F"The reasons for this Notice of Motion
OL,7,Fare as follows: Care in north Wales is
OL,8,Fin crisis with BCUHB now having the
OL,9,Fhighest numbers of preventable deaths
OL,10,Fin Wales ` Section 28 Coroners Reports
OL,11,F` of which many are directly
OL,12,Fattributed to prolonged waits in BCUHB
OL,13,FA&E departments," the letter stated.
OL,15,F"The strain being put on Conwy Social
OL,16,FCare department is unsustainable, and
OL,17,Fhealth outcomes for our Conwy
OL,18,Fresidents are deteriorating
OL,19,Funacceptably.
