OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,F"The residents of Conwy deserve safe
OL,7,Fand timely care in our hospitals and
OL,8,Fsecondary care settings, and for
OL,9,FPrimary Care to get the resources our
OL,10,FGPs need to deliver care in our
OL,11,Fcommunities."
OL,13,FCllr Fallon told the chamber that the
OL,14,Fsituation had "worsened", adding that
OL,15,Fthere "appeared to be a policy change"
OL,16,Fby the health board, placing patients
OL,17,Fin the corridors of wards at the major
OL,18,Fhospitals.
OL,20,FShe said the situation led to
OL,21,Fdiscussions by all six council leaders.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/15
