OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,F"It is completely unacceptable to
OL,7,Fthink that they are moving one
OL,8,Fsignificant issue in an emergency
OL,9,Fdepartment and actually then moving
OL,10,Fthat to the wards around the
OL,11,Fhospital," she said, adding that
OL,12,Fpatients being treated in corridors
OL,13,Fwhen they are unwell is 'humiliating'.
OL,15,F"This is a loss of dignity, and it's
OL,16,Fstripping patients of their self-
OL,17,Frespect, if this is happening, and
OL,18,Fit's completely unfair to our amazing
OL,19,Fstaff," Cllr Fallon said.
