OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,F"I'm going to stand up and be counted
OL,7,Fand jump up and down about this."
OL,9,FShe also called on Betsi Cadwaladr
OL,10,FUniversity Health Board to respond to
OL,11,Fthe six leaders.
OL,13,F"I think they've had a week now, and
OL,14,Fthe fact that we've had no response,
OL,15,Fit's really shocking. The fact that
OL,16,Fthe Health Minister hasn't responded,
OL,17,Fit's incredibly disappointing," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
