OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,F"Enough is enough. We can't have
OL,7,Fpatients lying in corridors dying,
OL,8,Fwhich I know is what has happened in
OL,9,Femergency departments, and that will
OL,10,Fhappen on the wards as well."
OL,12,FShe added: "In all the 15 years I've
OL,13,Fbeen a councillor, I don't think
OL,14,Fanything has made me quite as unhappy,
OL,15,Fcross, frustrated. I'm just generally
OL,16,Fsad that this is the state of affairs.
OL,17,FWe are not in a third world country."
