OL,3,C'Health emergency' declared by second
OL,4,Ccouncil in north Wales
OL,6,FTehmeena Ajmal, Chief Operating
OL,7,FOfficer at BCUHB, said: "We recognise
OL,8,Fthe serious pressures facing urgent
OL,9,Fand emergency care in North Wales and
OL,10,Fas a Board we are taking coordinated
OL,11,Faction across the health and social
OL,12,Fcare system, together with our Local
OL,13,FAuthority partners, to deliver the
OL,14,Frequired improvements. Reducing the
OL,15,Fuse of corridor care and improving
OL,16,Fpatient flow and discharge from
OL,17,Fhospital is a collective priority and
OL,18,Fhence this is the Health Board's top
OL,19,Foperational goal.
