OL,6,F"The Leaders of the six Local
OL,7,FAuthorities in North Wales have
OL,8,Fwritten to the Health Board outlining
OL,9,Ftheir concerns that a new policy may
OL,10,Fhave been introduced which facilitates
OL,11,Fthe routine use of corridor care on
OL,12,Fhospital wards across North Wales. We
OL,13,Fhave responded to this letter directly
OL,14,Fproviding reassurance that no such
OL,15,Fpolicy has been introduced.
